{"tid":367220,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"北海道住宿求教 (2)","createTime":"2017-08-20T14:57:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T17:00:40.000Z","uid":89538,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a4dc6e1282378998bc95a374cbbcde2c03d7f81d","tid":367220,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T14:57:29.000Z","msg":"Hello 話說小弟曾經做過伸手黨<br />\n依家痛改前非<br />\n但北海道真係太大,希望巴打們可以係交通同住宿上比D意見<br />\n<br />\n28/9 : 2點到新千歲,會去札幌玩下, 大通公園有個秋日祭,過一晚<br />\n29/9: 朝早JR去網走,睇能取珊瑚草(希望黎得切),求其過一晚<br />\nJR呢度唔知應該買唔買鐵路週遊卷好...<br />\n30/9: 去阿寒湖,順便玩埋個原住民火祭(千隻炬火&amp;衣優曼帖的火祭)<br />\n阿寒湖住一晚溫泉旅館 (鶴雅之翼好似好出名?)<br />\n1/10:搭巴士直接由阿寒湖去層雲峽,睇紅葉,又住一晚溫泉旅館<br />\n2/10: 去旭山動物園 同美瑛<br />\n3/10: 富良野 同埋睇下葡萄酒莊<br />\n4/10: 番札幌就住定係度幾日<br />\n5/10: 札幌 + 小樽<br />\n6/10: 定山溪<br />\n7/10: 洞爺湖,溫泉旅館,睇煙火大會<br />\n8/10:支芴湖紅葉祭 + 登別地獄谷<br />\n9/10:搭車番新千歲手信番香港<br />\n<br />\n問題:<br />\n1. 小弟唔係先駕,咁既情況有無咩PASS好用呢?定其實巴士都可以依賴?<br />\n2.一開波就去網走會唔會太遠?又成五個鐘JR,但又怕再遲會睇唔到珊瑚草...<br />\n3. 溫泉酒店有無D CP值高D既推介? 最怕中伏,太舊或者D野難食...<br />\n<br />\n請賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"584b5e04441900bc0098b8588e0118d54cd1aaf2","tid":367220,"uid":5218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:01:52.000Z","msg":"完全冇問題，完全係旅遊達人既玩法，先 save 底先。"},{"pid":"efe2d53977b3f8f556e3bddcc58d96fa9e23dea9","tid":367220,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T22:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f50979311a036bc14dceeb6800c170dd0d45f9f","tid":367220,"uid":10035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T23:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e91f9be9f63880c2dbc4979e2fe4ae5976939a","tid":367220,"uid":71502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75e7d8f2677bb564dbe7932eae4f4dc12267db21","tid":367220,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T11:42:33.000Z","msg":"黎啦 屌下我都好 對住宿同搭車都無乜諗頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b9b766ad3704de389495ad2938fa1f272a3717","tid":367220,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T11:59:15.000Z","msg":"洞爺湖乃之風"},{"pid":"0dd300e92fa8e2c1f42b5a0d0b070cf05f8a6b38","tid":367220,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:15:11.000Z","msg":"買pass要搭得多先抵<br />\n除咗去網走嗰程之外其他都唔太貴<br />\n買pass應該回唔到本"},{"pid":"3cb6964869d02cadf7908e076c22bd8300c2f786","tid":367220,"uid":63863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:17:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買pass要搭得多先抵<br />\n除咗去網走嗰程之外其他都唔太貴<br />\n買pass應該回唔到本</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買啦，幫下JR札幌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac1b25ad40784a9fad07e798d1d5b8aa3325bec","tid":367220,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:19:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>買pass要搭得多先抵<br />\n除咗去網走嗰程之外其他都唔太貴<br />\n買pass應該回唔到本</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買啦，幫下JR札幌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nJR好唔掂咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ee0785c3c99795b543a050e1cd34541cdc7ef8","tid":367220,"uid":90000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:25:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Hello 話說小弟曾經做過伸手黨<br />\n依家痛改前非<br />\n但北海道真係太大,希望巴打們可以係交通同住宿上比D意見<br />\n<br />\n28/9 : 2點到新千歲,會去札幌玩下, 大通公園有個秋日祭,過一晚<br />\n29/9: 朝早JR去網走,睇能取珊瑚草(希望黎得切),求其過一晚<br />\nJR呢度唔知應該買唔買鐵路週遊卷好...<br />\n30/9: 去阿寒湖,順便玩埋個原住民火祭(千隻炬火&amp;衣優曼帖的火祭)<br />\n阿寒湖住一晚溫泉旅館 (鶴雅之翼好似好出名?)<br />\n1/10:搭巴士直接由阿寒湖去層雲峽,睇紅葉,又住一晚溫泉旅館<br />\n2/10: 去旭山動物園 同美瑛<br />\n3/10: 富良野 同埋睇下葡萄酒莊<br />\n4/10: 番札幌就住定係度幾日<br />\n5/10: 札幌 + 小樽<br />\n6/10: 定山溪<br />\n7/10: 洞爺湖,溫泉旅館,睇煙火大會<br />\n8/10:支芴湖紅葉祭 + 登別地獄谷<br />\n9/10:搭車番新千歲手信番香港<br />\n<br />\n問題:<br />\n1. 小弟唔係先駕,咁既情況有無咩PASS好用呢?定其實巴士都可以依賴?<br />\n2.一開波就去網走會唔會太遠?又成五個鐘JR,但又怕再遲會睇唔到珊瑚草...<br />\n3. 溫泉酒店有無D CP值高D既推介? 最怕中伏,太舊或者D野難食...<br />\n<br />\n請賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2 新千歲睇下有冇機去網走女滿別,唔洗係札幌坐5個鐘JR 咁辛苦。"},{"pid":"6a09848ecc53a9d506b241c34048cf6545a175ba","tid":367220,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:34:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>買pass要搭得多先抵<br />\n除咗去網走嗰程之外其他都唔太貴<br />\n買pass應該回唔到本</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買啦，幫下JR札幌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nJR好唔掂咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n舊年蝕左差唔多400億Yen <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c77faaab52badcd18b22af16545c669a82b2ee6","tid":367220,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:50:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>買pass要搭得多先抵<br />\n除咗去網走嗰程之外其他都唔太貴<br />\n買pass應該回唔到本</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買啦，幫下JR札幌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nJR好唔掂咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n舊年蝕左差唔多400億Yen <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" cla